WHAT IS IT?
-----------

  A major electrical overload messed up the lighting system in a
high-rise building in downtown Montreal and it is your job to fix
things... the goal is to turn off ALL the lights in that building.

  If this sounds simple, it shouldn't, because as you turn off
some lights, others (as many as 12 lights), are randomly turned
on or off, depending on their state.

  Can you complete the game without getting a big headache?!

  Have fun!

